      "author": "GiannisKoukounas (Giannis Koukounas)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/dedwards\">@dedwards</a> !</p>\n<p>The pivot view can certainly be exported, similarly to all widgets.</p>\n<p>All you need to do is export your dashboard to PDF.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/3/d3fedb3506d344dd3bde6594323af18fc10e5338.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"440\" height=\"489\" /></p>\n<p>Let me know if this helps!</p>\n<p>Best Regards,<br />\nGiannis, Implementation Consultant at <a href=\"http://thespelas.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">thespelas.com</a></p>"
    },
